  "text": "Stationary phase EHEC or EAEC cultures were diluted 1:100 with DMEM +0.2% glucose and various indole derivatives added. Bacterial solutions were added to tissue culture coated 96 well plates (Corning) and incubated at 37C for 48 hours. Biofilm formation was visualized by crystal violet staining as described above, and formation or loss of biofilm was measured at OD 595 . Motility in soft agar was measured as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
